These are instructions for installing the mncronsafe module into a Drupal 6
website.

################################################################################
  Quick Install
################################################################################

# cd /var/www/mninews/sites/all/modules
# svn checkout http://10.1.1.40/svn/jcerda/sites/modules/mncronsafe
# chown -R 1080:mninews mncronsafe

// Go to:  admin/build/modules
// Enable the "MNI Cron Safe" module

// Should you want to adjust the primary ip address or add additional
// modules to disable, please modify the file:
//     /var/www/mninews/sites/all/modules/mncronsafe/production.cfg
